    "Stash_IrvingtonMap2_Text2": "你會為",
    "Stash_IrvingtonMap2_Text3": "你對安所做的付出代價",
    "Stash_IrvingtonMap3_Text1": "別跑! 他們會追你的",
    "Stash_IrvingtonMap3_Text2": "如果需要, 用無線電聯絡我們",
    "Stash_IrvingtonMap3_Text3": "學校",
    "Stash_IrvingtonMap3_Text4": "屍群",
    "Stash_IrvingtonMap4_Text1": "戰爭多麼古怪離奇",
    "Stash_IrvingtonMap4_Text2": "你所擊倒的那傢伙",
    "Stash_IrvingtonMap4_Text3": "若在酒館相遇, 本會請他喝一杯",
    "Stash_IrvingtonMap4_Text4": "或借他半克朗銀幣",
    "Stash_IrvingtonMap5_Text1": "這裡應該有食物",
    "Stash_IrvingtonMap5_Text2": "除非特蕾莎把它們全拿走了",
    "Stash_IrvingtonMap6_Text1": "東西可能在這裡",
    "Stash_IrvingtonMap6_Text2": "但要小心",
    "Stash_IrvingtonMap8_Text1": "餐館",
    "Stash_IrvingtonMap8_Text2": "洗衣店",
    "Stash_IrvingtonMap8_Text3": "我不會是唯一剩下的人",
    "Stash_IrvingtonMap9_Text1": "我們可以在這裡加強防禦",
    "Stash_IrvingtonMap9_Text2": "一切都會好起來的!",
    "Stash_IrvingtonMap10_Text1": "歐文頓",
    "Stash_IrvingtonMap10_Text2": "我們會在這裡",
    "Stash_WorldMap1_Text1": "卡拉會幫忙的",
    "Stash_WorldMap1_Text2": "慢點開車",
    "Stash_WorldMap2_Text1": "很好的基地",
    "Stash_WorldMap2_Text11": "到達時先設定路障!",
    "Stash_WorldMap2_Text12": "給你藏了一些槍",
    "Stash_WorldMap3_Text1": "這裡有丙烷罐",
    "Stash_WorldMap3_Text11": "你需要它",
    "Stash_WorldMap4_Text1": "亞娜說",
    "Stash_WorldMap4_Text11": "這是那個女人住的地方",
    "Stash_WorldMap4_Text12": "也許她會幫助我們",
    "Stash_WorldMap5_Text1": "保利把東西放在這裡了",
    "Stash_WorldMap5_Text11": "不要被發現了",
    "Stash_WorldMap5_Text12": "別忘了燒掉這張地圖!!!",
    "Stash_WorldMap6_Text1": "這裡有好東西",
    "Stash_WorldMap6_Text2": "用於搜尋 - 太大而難以設防",
    "Stash_WorldMap6_Text3": "安迪",
    "Stash_WorldMap7_Text1": "在這裡",
    "Stash_WorldMap7_Text2": "全被感染了",
    "Stash_WorldMap7_Text21": "它們都是從哪裡來的",
    "Stash_WorldMap9_Text1": "貨運站",
    "Stash_WorldMap9_Text2": "到處都是箱子, 可以裝滿東西",
    "Stash_WorldMap9_Text3": "辦公室, 什麼都沒有",
    "Stash_WorldMap9_Text4": "倉庫",
    "Stash_WorldMap9_Text5": "馬爾德勞",
    "Stash_WorldMap9_Text6": "這裡的火車全都沒法開? ? ?",
    "Stash_WorldMap10_Text1": "加油站",
    "Stash_WorldMap10_Text2": "服裝店",
    "Stash_WorldMap10_Text3": "斯皮福餐廳",
    "Stash_WorldMap10_Text4": "汽車",
    "Stash_WorldMap11_Text1": "2 號塔上的 3 號天線 - 丟失訊號",
    "Stash_WorldMap11_Text11": "在 6 GHz 頻段上丟失訊號 - 電源問題",
    "Stash_WorldMap11_Text2": "讓總部和列剋星敦一起測試",
    "Stash_WorldMap12_Text1": "大型露營地",
    "Stash_WorldMap12_Text11": "我們需要一切 (簡需要的藥丸除外)",
    "Stash_WorldMap12_Text2": "我們很快就能坐在火堆旁",
    "Stash_WorldMap12_Text21": "放聲高歌",
    "Stash_WorldMap13_Text1": "哈爾, 我知道這很難",
    "Stash_WorldMap13_Text11": "但你真的該走了",
    "Stash_WorldMap13_Text12": "寶拉, 我們在這裡",
    "Stash_WorldMap14_Text1": "奶奶",
    "Stash_WorldMap14_Text2": "爸爸在這裡",
